Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Can either of you\Nthink of the kind of job
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,that I might be qualified for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Yamaji.\NI bet he'll have some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I could be wrong,\Nbut I think it's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP OWNER 3A]\NThank you. Come again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN 3A]\NOh, good morning, Yamaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Just making sure\NYoko's doors are secure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your back\Nstill bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Lemme help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA]\NMiss Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,--Good morning!\N--Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It's perfect weather\Nfor a picnic today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It is lovely out, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI don't know for how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard there's\Na typhoon coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NThat wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Something about it\Nmakes me uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NThis is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Much better than that awful\Nweather we had last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was terrible, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad we're able\Nto eat outside again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.04,Main,,0,0,0,,This is usually your\Nfavorite time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You brought your own lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you prefer to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep, but I burned\Nthrough my lunch allowance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,for the month already, so\Nthis is what I'm stuck with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhat did you spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Well I developed a\Npretty expensive habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I got hooked on sea urchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.89,Main,,0,0,0,,They say all it takes\Nis just a little taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NMan! Being broke is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should get\Na job or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Like where you do manual\Nlabor in exchange for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWell, that's the gist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of\Njob would be best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I could work at a cake shop.\NOr maybe a bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Or a café! That could be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hoping that\Nthey're going to pay you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,with money or with food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Either will work, really.\NI'm not picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat gives me an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of being destitute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I may have to consider\Ngetting a job myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Can either of you\Nthink of the kind of job
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,that I might be qualified for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko wants to work?\NHow would that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:22.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHere's your menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't take too long deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are,\Nordering me around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Do I look like a servant to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want coffee so\Nbadly, refill it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Not good at all. Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Yamaji.\NI bet he'll have some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't he pop out of his\Nstalker hiding place about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,"My poor Miss Yoko!" Right?\N[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NFutaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Wow!\NDid we get lucky or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I've heard about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been open that long,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,but I've really been\Nwanting to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,An adorable little cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What could be better\Nthan this, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have my\Ncake and eat it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You know it's a job,\Nnot a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you two should\Ngo on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You want a job, don't you?\NThis is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And we'll be with you,\Nso don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NWhat a cute little shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! So yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. I haven't\Nhad cake in so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I could be wrong,\Nbut I think it's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! I was afraid\Nyou would say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like it leads\Ninto the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see anybody in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] The trail disappears\Nbehind this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThis is simply horrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NIs that a real body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I think her hand just moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a zombie invasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoops. That was\Nvery careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a severe\Ncraving for sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,and I thought this berry\Njam would be just the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,to satisfy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I must've fallen asleep\Nwhile eating again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Standing up with\Nyour eyes wide open?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It really is you, Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But what in the world\Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hello, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She worked for my family\Nbefore, well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,My name is Shino Sonobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I used to be the\NNishikawa family's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI enjoy making sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:41.75,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's one of the\Nfew things I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Losing my maid position\Ngave me a new opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I was able to further\Nmy abilities as a baker
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,and open my very own shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat's excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't think I've\Never met a real maid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.77,Main,,0,0,0,,So you went from\Nworking for them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.77,Main,,0,0,0,,to owning your own business?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't believe we\Nhave been introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to meet\Nmy two new friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.\NI'm Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, that was\Njust quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone\Nwho knows "Miss Yoko"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,is surprised that\Nshe has friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got a funny way\Nof showing you're surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,The idea of working\Nat a place owned by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,someone you know must\Nmake you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NIt certainly does!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're suggesting Miss Yoko\Nwould work at my shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYes! That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,...if you think I'm qualified\Nfor the position, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, Miss Yoko,\NI'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSomebody is counting on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[echoes]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NDon't forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I want a job here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NOh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to hire you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,A friend of Miss Yoko's\Nwould be very amu--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, very dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:55.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you here for a job, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Me? No, I'm good. But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that?\NMilk bottle caps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nyou're doing, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NYamaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Good. Our milk delivery is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You can just put it all\Nin the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NDon't change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't answered\Nmy question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko isn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She can't have a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts\Njust thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I'm a little\Nworried too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm already having\Na hard enough time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,arranging my schedule so\NI can keep an eye on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need you\Ncomplicating things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NBy the way, Mitsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,thanks for helping me\Nfind this property.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You helped her\Nget this shop set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a job at a real\Nestate agency, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly force\NMiss Yoko to work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I want her to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, Sonobe says\Nshe's counting on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No disrespect, but you don't\Nknow that you're getting into.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Careful, you might accidentally\Nhurt somebody, Sonobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I was only swatting at a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems there are a\Nlot of flies around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop this despicable\Ndisplay this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Put those utensils down\Nand behave yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Jeez. That was\Nkinda scary, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like the most\Nnurturing work environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry you had\Nto see them act so shamefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should\Ntry looking around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,for a different place to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And who knows,\Nthere might be other ways
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.30,Main,,0,0,0,,for you to make money\Nbesides working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP OWNER 3A]\NThank you. Come again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Now that's what\NI'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] I ate a mountain of\Ndumplings and got paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll make it\Nthrough this month
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,without getting a job after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI figured you could do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,but I had no idea\Nit would be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] I have to admit,\NI'm a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing\NI'm particularly good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on!\NI'm sure that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't beat\Nyourself up so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of\Nthings that you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what kind of job
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,would be right for\Nsomebody like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You could work as a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,At a themed restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] You know, a place\Nwhere the servers all act
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.81,Main,,0,0,0,,a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a cafe where the\Nwaitresses are really snobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Is that a thing?\NDo they really have those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI'm sure they do somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys like weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NHold on... I'm snobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NReally, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You make the best dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHOP OWNER 3A]\NThank you. Come again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYou'll bankrupt that poor man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody's forcing him\Nto offer prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna take this\Nand buy something yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're still hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.97,Main,,0,0,0,,How 'bout the maid's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Our last experience\Nthere wasn't the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.23,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm not gonna lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The cakes she gave us\Nwere pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThey were more than good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It was like having\Na taste of maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't even know\Nwhat that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Secret Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to\Nsee you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWha--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not wearing\Na maid outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not a uniform.\NI just like wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] It seemed far\Nless daunting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,to work for somebody\Nwho I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And when I found out Yamaji\Nwould be working here, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew I would feel\Nright at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOf course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] I wonder how\Nhis stomach is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's great\Nyou got a job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Working for a friend\Nsounds like a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe seems really young\Nto own her own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess she must be\Nsome kind of prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What is she, 18?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't blame you for thinking\Nthat, given her appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're way off the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think she's\Nin her early thirties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NYou're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,There seems to be an\Nempty spot at the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,so I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NSo, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it true you're\Nreally in your thirties?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting a job is\Na big step for Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Is she doing well here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:23.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:24.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Since it's a small shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,the menu wasn't\Ntoo difficult to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The customers are very friendly.\NAnd the food is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should go\Nand check on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be back out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's actually a good worker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta admit I'm\Npretty impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Not everybody gets the\Nopportunity to hire someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,who once hired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what a\Nthrilling experience it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:54.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] The look on their\Nfaces when they walked in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they\Nthought when they saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet they were surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it was nice\Nto see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to stay\Nas long as you would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't rush on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I have some freshly baked\Ntreats if you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NOh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll take two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] The presence of young\Npeople is invigorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel as if I\Ncan eat so much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Like it vicariously\Nraises my metabolism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUm, she's joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Because that's the\Nmost ridiculous thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't be\Nsurprised to find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NOh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've kinda been hanging\Nout for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What, have you been\Nhiding somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I only come in the morning\Nto help bake the first cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I just stopped by to\Nsee how things were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,May I be of any assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,He must be one of\Nthose crazy workaholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,He's exactly the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Shows up without any warning,\Ngets everything done,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,and then moves on\Nto the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds\Njust like him all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Just between us, I honestly\Ncan't stand people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,They make me sick to my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] But anyway, tell\Nme about high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It must be fun. Is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Kinda. Lunch is fun, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,But mainly, we're all\Ngoing there to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NFascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NMiss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you've worked\Nso hard today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,you can end your\Nshift a bit early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsugu is still here\Nif I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not really here.\NI just work in the mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool! We can walk\Nhome together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:44.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's surprising how\Nexhausted you can get
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,just from standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You're doing a whole lot\Nmore than just standing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it weird to serve customers\Nafter being waited on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,your whole life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's difficult,\Nbut I manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, did you think I would\Nyell at them or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] So you're raking\Nin the big bucks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Maybe you can eliminate\Nbread crusts from your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NWhy would I want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,They're cheap and plentiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Not to mention delicious\Nwhen topped with mayonnaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA, HAYAMA]\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you\Nladies again very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww... I'm gonna\Nstarve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,One more class to go\Nbefore lunch, so you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NFutaba! Hayama! Futaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Is somebody calling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, that voice.\NI know it from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Turn around. I'm\Nstanding right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could borrow a\Nmoment of your time, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWha--Wha--Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] What in the\Nworld are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO giggles]\NOops. Did I startle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That isn't the problem!\NNow, where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NOh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I made it after\Nyou left yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't too difficult, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.24,Main,,0,0,0,,The pattern itself is\Na very simplistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NYou know, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I asked\Nthe wrong question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Start by telling us\Nwhat you're doing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,And why aren't you\Nwearing the maid outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You're really not helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I change clothes\Nsometimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NCan we focus, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what I would\Nlike to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nat our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm simply trying\Nto be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.47,Main,,0,0,0,,What, fan service?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] That would work\Nbetter with the maid getup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we drop that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, there's something\NI want to give Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] I went overboard\Nwith my prep today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she might enjoy it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,so I boxed some of the\Nextra food up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you made her lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThere, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I have a perfectly good\Nexplanation for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope. There's just\Nno good explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,for a woman in her thirties\Ntrying to masquerade
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,as a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[bell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There goes the bell.\NWe should get to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, Sonobe,\Nwhat are you going to--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NHey! She disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NShe's a poltergeist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I have to wait until\Nlunchtime to give this to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll just explore\Nthe school until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThe feel of a linoleum floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The scent of youth!\NSo, so, delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, what a lovely view!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI love being up this high!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so empowering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And school uniforms\Nare perfectly designed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,to catch this breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[TEACHER 3A] The subjunctive\Nmood is easily identified
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,by the use of a clause\Nbeginning in "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It is used to express...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, is it just me,\Nor does it sound like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,the school's being\Nattacked by Tarzan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the poltergeist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[P.E. TEACHER 2A] All right!\NEverybody pair off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Get those stretches done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on!\NStop all the chit-chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, first things first,\Nwe need to find Sonobe--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] So it appears that\Nyou are schoolmates,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,but not actually classmates\Nwith Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nwhy you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to eat\Nlunch with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,so I made a uniform\Nand came to your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NWhich is crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA] Yoko doesn't\Nseem too fazed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,When one works with Sonobe,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,one accepts that\Nstrange things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA, FUTABA]\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThere's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Help yourselves to\Nwhatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!\NDon't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NI made potato salad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,with a generous amount\Nof mayonnaise, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You do know\Nwhat I like, Sonobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\N'Kay, you handed over her lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can\Njust get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so nice of you\Nto think of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHere you are, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's from your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you draw these\Ncute little pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought the letter\Nwould be more enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.94,Main,,0,0,0,,if it were illustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks!\NThat's very sweet of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NCareful, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to make sure\Nyou're having balanced meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA]\NGive me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Like you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I eat plenty of bread, rice,\Nmeat, and veggies every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Sure, but you're\Nnot supposed to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.37,Main,,0,0,0,,truckloads of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA gasps]\NI don't eat that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to get back to\Nthe shop, so I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO] Hayama, Futaba,\NI leave Miss Yoko to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Please take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sonobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NWhat is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYamaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Prancing about in a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NGet back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure at first,\Nbut I think she came here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,because she was\Nworried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She's pretty weird, but she\Nseems like a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NYes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NHere you go. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious cakes.\NNew specials every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, take a flier with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NSonobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NMiss Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you mind\Ntelling me what exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,you think you're doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NWould you like one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] No, I wouldn't!\NThat's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUTABA]\NEasy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[HAYAMA] Maybe you should\Ntake a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:03.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO] You really think\Nit's okay to be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:04.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm quite confident\Nthat nobody can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NCan tell what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That you're a grown woman\Nhanging out at a high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NNo, this uniform is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[YOKO]\NThat isn't the issue either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Sonobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\NThis is Maid Angel Super Shino!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.18,0:23:51.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you enjoyed this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,From this week on, I'll be here\Nto put a smile on your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Please support me!\NYou will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:23:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I will fight\Nwith what I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Perish! Unpaid overtime!\NIllegal uploading!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[YAMAJI]\NWhat year are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[SHINO]\N2016.
